articles.description: Alessandro Lever scored 29 points and Damari Milstead sank two free throws with 21 seconds remaining as third-seeded Grand Canyon recovered from first-half jitters in the school's first trip to the post season and defeat No. 5 seed Missouri-Kansas...
articles.headline: Grand Canyon wins first post-season game, downs UMKC 77-74

articles.description: T.J. Shorts II scored 15 points, including the clinching free throws with one second left, Joe Mooney had a career-high 15 points and top-seeded UC Davis edged eighth-seeded UC Riverside 70-66 on Thursday in the opening game of the Big West Conference...
articles.headline: Shorts, Mooney lead Davis over Riverside 70-66 in BWC opener

videos.description: Wagner's AJ Sumbry makes the strong two-handed dunk off of the great backdoor pass from Blake Francis.
videos.headline: Wagner's Sumbry throws it down with authority

videos.description: LIU-Brooklyn's Joel Hernandez slaps Wagner's JoJo Cooper's attempt off the backboard.
videos.headline: Crean: 'No soup for you' after Joel Hernandez's block

videos.description: LIU-Brooklyn's Joel Hernandez grabs the offensive rebound and draws contact after the basket during a 17-point first half against Wagner.
videos.headline: Hernandez drops 19 in 1st half

videos.description: LIU-Brooklyn's head coach Derek Kellogg praises Joel Hernandez's first-half performance, after Hernandez drops 19 in the first half against Wagner in the NEC title game.
videos.headline: Joel Hernandez 'has the heart of a champion'

videos.description: LIU-Brooklyn's Joel Hernandez puts the ball on a string to get it out to Zach Coleman who knocks down the three-pointer.
videos.headline: Hernandez finds Coleman in the corner for 3

videos.headline: LIU's Clark beats double team

videos.description: LIU-Brooklyn storms the court at Wagner, after the Blackbirds take down the Seahawks 71-61 in the NEC Championship game.
videos.headline: LIU celebrates NEC victory

videos.description: Joel Hernandez expresses his feelings on winning the NEC Championship and his thoughts on going to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: LIU-Brooklyn's Hernandez: 'This is a dream come true'
